genresAdvancedInfo.name: macau pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Macau pop is a genre of popular music that originated in Macau. It features a blend of Chinese and Western musical influences, with catchy melodies, upbeat rhythms, and lively instrumentation. The lyrics often reflect the culture and traditions of Macau, with themes such as love, family, and the beauty of nature. Artists such as Joey Yung and Nicholas Tse are popular representatives of this genre.
